title: Freecell 2006 6 [full version]
description:
ABOUT THIS GAME:

Freecell 2006 is the highest rated Freecell on the Web. It has a
lot of cool features like 3 million starting positions, undo,
redo, undoall, redoall, replay forward and back, snapshot,
favorites, autosave, adjustable card speed, game saving, global
and general history, detailed scoreboard with statistics and top
score. Version 6 may include unspecified updates, enhancements,
or bug fixes.
